&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and ship full-stack features across the product as you ramp up on the platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a thorough understanding of our systems, data models, and business logic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-leverage automation opportunities as you learn how the platform works&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and build AI agents and automated workflows using modern AI tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate LLMs into product workflows in ways that are reliable and production-safe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate, iterate, and improve AI systems based on real-world performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product and engineering to solve user-facing problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define what effective, responsible AI engineering looks like at our company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
