&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with LLM APIs (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.), vector databases, RAG pipelines, and agent frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong software engineering fundamentals, including system design, testing, debugging, and clean code practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator who can work across product and engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
